ğŸ“Œ 1. React Basics
âœ… What is React?
React is a JavaScript library for building user interfaces.

It allows building Single Page Applications (SPA) â€“ meaning the page doesnâ€™t reload for every navigation. Instead, React dynamically updates parts of the page using Virtual DOM.

This makes apps faster and smoother.
